                    div.flex.items.center.justify-between
                        a.text-indigo-200.text-xs.floating(class="hover:text-crimson-100 hover:underline hover:decoration-crimson-100" href="/auth/login") ¿Ya tienes cuenta? 
                            span.text-xs.text-black_white-100 Inicia Sesión
                        a.text-indigo-200.text-xs.floating(class="hover:text-crimson-100 hover:underline hover:decoration-crimson-100" href="/auth/passswordRecovery") Olvide mi contraseña

                    input(class="w-full bg-crimson-500 hover:bg-crimson-800 text-black_white-100 font-bold py-3 cursor-pointer rounded-lg" type="submit" value="Crear Cuenta")

            style.
                    @keyframes float {
                        0%, 100% {
                            transform: translateY(0);
                        }
                        50% {
                            transform: translateY(-5px);
                        }
                    }

                    .floating {
                        display: inline-block;
                        animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite; 
                    }
                    @keyframes text-pulse {
                    0%, 100% {
                        color: #c7d2fe; /* Color base */
                        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #c7d2fe, 0 0 20px #c7d2fe, 0 0 40px rgba(199, 210, 254, 0.5);
                    }
                    50% {
                        color: #ffffff; /* Más brillante */
                        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #ffffff, 0 0 60px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
                    }
                    }

                    /* Clase para texto pulsante */
                    .text-pulse {
                        animation: text-pulse 3s infinite ease-in-out; /* Duración ajustable */
                    }
                    @keyframes box-shadow-pulse {
                    0%, 100% {
                        box-shadow: 0 0 15px 5px rgba(199, 210, 254, 0.5), 0 0 30px 10px rgba(30, 27, 75, 0.5);
                    }
                    50% {
                        box-shadow: 0 0 20px 10px rgba(200, 45, 109, 0.8), 0 0 40px 15px rgba(200, 45, 109, 0.7);
                    }
                    }

                    /* Clase para formularios pulsantes */
                    .form-pulse {
                        animation: box-shadow-pulse 10s infinite ease-in-out; /* Duración ajustable */
                    }

